  "doc_id": "30451",
  "text": "Branch tunnel position on the desired greater curve is permitted with Bolton's patented self-orienting precurved nitinol guidewire lumen, which enables alignment of the arch graft's cannulation window to the primary curve of the arch. [CITATION_1] In our opinion, this technology allows a wider degree of manoeuvrability during the deployment of the device, and in particular during the alignment of the fenestrations and the epiaortic vessels.",
  "correct_citation": {
